# web-change-checker
# 
# configuration file, contains one site to watch on each line
# format of a line is:
#   site;striphtml;email;email;...
#
# where
#   'site' is a valid URL to be watched for updates
#   'striphtml' if "yes" will eliminate html <tags> and replace html entities (i.e. &amp;) with unicode
#   'email' is any valid mail address to be notified on change

http://google.com/;yes;mail@example.com;mail2@example.com
